snippet.title: PUBG MOBILE 1ST YEAR ANNIVERSARY PARTY!
snippet.description:
Today is PUBG MOBILE’s birthday! We are going to have fun with Alan Walker and YouTube Space New York along with Lisa Peachy, Scotty Sire and FaZe Adapt! Alan Walker will perform his new song “On My Way” for the first time. Let’s get the party started!

Download PUBG MOBILE for free: http://bit.ly/2HBObOF
